title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported without any exception when the table contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
SR: To reproduce the issue:  1. Open the attached report.  2. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.  3. Preview the report.  4. Try to export the data from the table and observe if an exception is thrown.
